## Summary: Recommended Technology Stack

| Category | Web App | CEP Panel |
|----------|---------|-----------|
| **Framework** | Next.js 15 + React 19 | Bolt CEP + React |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui | Spectrum CSS (minimal) |
| **State (Server)** | TanStack Query v5 | TanStack Query v5 |
| **State (Client)** | Zustand | Zustand |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Lucide React |
| **Animation** | Framer Motion | CSS Animations |
| **Audio** | wavesurfer.js | wavesurfer.js (lightweight) |
| **Upload** | react-dropzone | Native file input |
| **Forms** | React Hook Form + Zod | React Hook Form |
| **Skeletons** | react-loading-skeleton | Custom CSS |

